{"tid":2381522,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"sales) 成立第七年 員工折扣分享群組","createTime":"2021-01-26T15:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T10:19:16.000Z","uid":75218,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7383dfc0657928251ce2ec87688ee8a4d6f360a6","tid":2381522,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"各位好，員工折扣谷今年係第七年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝曬各位巴打絲打互相分享<br />\n呢個群組先可以搞到今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去2年為咗保障本身谷入面既人，變到好少加人，因為我地始終係用whatsapp群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今年 ，因為WhatsApp on99既關係， 我地決定全面改用 TELEGRAM 群組， 亦都會正式開始重新加人<br />\n<br />\n。暫時我地有大概500位成員<br />\n。加入黎既條件好簡單，就係會share自己提供到既折扣<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就填左下邊份form ，等我地加你入去啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/16Lov4SQySsQH_BvgQYkTJO1TcAybv5rsLnGLv5tzp6o/edit?usp=drive_open\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F16Lov4SQySsQH_BvgQYkTJO1TcAybv5rsLnGLv5tzp6o%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrive_open&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=31b5d844\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/16Lov4SQySsQH_BvgQYkTJO1TcAybv5rsLnGLv5tzp6o/edit?usp=drive_open</a>"},{"pid":"2d0a053b423ff696c907c8aba5d839452f1afdc4","tid":2381522,"uid":250271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"我們已經收到您回覆的表單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5b6ba421a5ca89dedabbc6aaa8f8f5df8ccff","tid":2381522,"uid":75218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d0a053b423ff696c907c8aba5d839452f1afdc4","tid":2381522,"uid":250271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"我們已經收到您回覆的表單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:21:46.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"5088513078029